<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by shashi:
[B]Well I paid about 100pp in one sitting for my bars to be enchanted... but then again I found a really nice enchanter that was willing to sit down with me for a few minutes and enchant like 8 bars for me at once. He didn't even ask for a specific amount, just asked me to donate what it was worth to me and so I handed him what was left in my pp slot after buying all the bars. (Enchant Plat is not a cheap spell mana-wise btw.)

On the most part tho, as long as you tell the enchanter what your using them for they'll be more than happy to enchant for free or a small donation. Some have even bought the bars for me so I could get a better price.  :)

Cinlai Shaestari
Lanys T'Vyl[/B][/QUOTE]

